From 0260ad0707acc6b76331592874c0828cdab62a69 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Matthew Vance <yinzara@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 11 Nov 2025 01:55:22 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] bluetooth: l2cap: Add debug logging for address type in
 getname

Add printk debugging to l2cap_sock_getname to track address type
assignment for peer connections. This helps diagnose issues where
bluetoothd receives incorrect address types causing device registration
failures.

Logs:
- LE_LINK connections with dst_type
- BR/EDR connections
- Missing hcon cases
---
